         <abstract><p>The <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān</foreign> is a collection of hymns to be chanted on Sundays in praise of the Blessed Virgin.
            It is part of the Ethiopic <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2701Dawit">psalter</ref>, copied following the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2509Weddas"/>
